INFO: 

Kill running D-BUS service: 

  "pkill -f augeasSambaService.rb"

Log out from running D-BUS service to "/var/log/messages" with:

  require  "syslog"
  Syslog.open($0, Syslog::LOG_PID | Syslog::LOG_CONS) { |s| s.info "YOUR MESSAGE" }





